data.description: Exquisite one of a kind custom home w/many designer features. Feels like you are on top of the world! Look out your expansive windows at the Panoramic views of the City, Oak Harbor Bay & Mt Baker! Open concept living w/vaulted ceilings & 2 wrap around decks. Gourmet kitchen, walk in pantry, stainless steel appliances & large skylights. Generous main bedroom w/exceptional views & private balcony. Upper floor presents spacious loft, 4th bedroom, office, playroom; bring your imagination! Bottom floor w/2 private bedrooms & full bath. Need storage space? You found it! This home offers a one of a kind 725 sq ft easy walk in access storage/shop or you name it! 3-car garage w/40 ft bay & 11 ft garage doors. Low maintenance yard. Easy walk to town!
